DTLA Penthouse in Historic Banking District

Los Angeles, California, United States
Show all photos
Entire loft hosted by Kim
4 guests 2 bedrooms 1 bed 2 baths
Enhanced Clean
This host committed to Airbnb's 5-step enhanced cleaning process.
A gorgeous Modern, Stylish & Luxury loft set inside a charming & completely renovated building in DTLA. It has all the essentials you need to make your stay in LA a special one! 24 hr security, a hot tub, BBQ and a common area lounge. Within walking distance or short drive from the Staples Center, LA Convention Center and all the best restaurants, bars, shops and galleries. This is truly a gem!
